.row.justify-content-md-center
  .col-12.col-md-6
    h1.text-center.mt-5 style='font-weight: bold' Turn your clutter into cash

    form id="upload-widget" method="post" action="/images" class="dropzone mt-4"

    .text-center.mt-3
      i class="fa fa-angle-up fa-2x animated"
